    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri'; font-size: 11pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; margin-bottom: 6pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Calibri'; font-size: 11pt;}\n.html-preview .a5 {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Манзил:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс номи ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">даъвони таъминлаш чорасини бекор қилиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 60px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> судига даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича даъвогар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> менга нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ҳақидаги даъво аризаси билан мурожаат этган. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Суднинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#11}Даъвони таъминлаш чорасини қўллаш тўғрисида ажрим қабул қилинган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> кундаги ажрими билан </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Суд ажримига асосан тайинланган даъвони таъминлаш чораси тури</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> тарзидаги </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">даъвони таъминлаш чораси қўлланилган. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Суднинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Суд томонидан ҳал қилув қарори қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">кунидаги ҳал қилув қарори билан даъвогарнинг даъво талабларини қаноатлантириш рад этилди. <span class=\"leading\"></span>Суднинг ҳал қилув қарори </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Суднинг ҳал қилув қарори кучга кирган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> кунидан эътиборан қонуний кучга кирган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Лекин суд <span class=\"leading\"></span>томонидан даъвони таъминлаш чораларини бекор қилиш масаласи ҳал қилинмасдан қолган. Бу ҳолат мени ўзимга тегишли мол-мулкдан фойдаланиш ва уларни тасарруф этиш борасидаги ҳуқуқларимни амалга оширишимга тўсқинлик қилмоқда. <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Юқоридагилардан келиб чиқиб, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал кодексининг 99-моддасига асосланиб, даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#9}Иш бўйича даъвогар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">нинг менга нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#10}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> тўғрисидаги иқтисодий иш бўйича суднинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#11}Даъвони таъминлаш чорасини қўллаш тўғрисида ажрим қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> кунидаги ажрими билан қўлланилган даъвони таъминлаш чорасини бекор қилишингизни. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Илова: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">1. Ариза нусхаси</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">2. Суднинг ҳал қилув қарори нусхаси</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс раҳбарининг ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">имзо</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
